# UD Marketing Tools

> Free browser-based SEO, content, campaign tracking, QR, and marketing utility tools for creators, students, marketers, and small businesses.

UD Marketing Tools provides simple online utilities and practical guides for writing, search optimization, campaign tracking, QR generation, and marketing calculations. The site is designed for quick, no-login workflows.

## Main Pages - [Home](https://udmarketing.online/) - Overview of UD Marketing Tools. - [Tools](https://udmarketing.online/tools/) - All free marketing and SEO tools. - [Articles](https://udmarketing.online/articles/) - Practical guides for SEO, content, analytics, and campaign tracking. - [About](https://udmarketing.online/about/) - Information about the site. - [Contact](https://udmarketing.online/contact/) - Contact page.

## Tools - [Word Counter](https://udmarketing.online/tools/word-counter/) - Check word count, character count, sentence count, paragraphs, and reading time. - [Readability Checker](https://udmarketing.online/tools/readability-checker/) - Review how easy your text is to read and improve clarity. - [Keyword Density Checker](https://udmarketing.online/tools/keyword-density-checker/) - Check keyword frequency and spot repeated terms in SEO content. - [Meta Tag Generator](https://udmarketing.online/tools/meta-tag-generator/) - Create meta titles, descriptions, Open Graph tags, and Twitter card tags. - [CPC and ROAS Calculator](https://udmarketing.online/tools/cpc-roas-calculator/) - Estimate campaign efficiency, ad spend, and return on ad spend. - [UTM Builder](https://udmarketing.online/tools/utm-builder/) - Build UTM tracking links for campaigns, ads, social posts, and email. - [QR Code Generator](https://udmarketing.online/tools/qr-code-generator/) - Generate QR codes for links, landing pages, forms, and promotions. - [QR and Barcode Scanner](https://udmarketing.online/tools/qr-barcode-scanner/) - Scan QR codes and supported barcodes using a camera.

